CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1958, pg. 5 reads: "4. Dan-Dee Pretzel Company chose three lovely ladies to show three of their tasty products. Left to right: Mabel B. Mills, Arlene Thompson and Betty Moore.  Representatives Catherine Delvin, Fanny Lucas, Herb Shork, and Truman J. Fisher are not shown"
TitMainTitle: Two men and woman standing in Dan Dee Pretzel and Potato Chips booth holding products for woman to view, in Syria Mosque for the 1958 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
